            cheaper, more secure, or more readily accessible to anyone, anywhere. Accepting Bitcoin was the
            obvious choice, and Cubits helped us make this choice a reality. ”
          cite.member__cite
            | Peter Kral <br> CTO at Wikando
  //END testimonial

